---
import Container from './Container.astro'
import CustomEmail from './CustomEmail.astro'
import AnimationIsla from './homePage/AnimationIsla.astro'
---

<footer
	class="relative h-[900px] bg-pampas-50 md:h-[700px]"
	style={{ clipPath: 'polygon(0% 0, 100% 0%, 100% 100%, 0 100%)' }}
>
	<div class="relative -top-[100vh] h-[calc(100vh+900px)] md:h-[calc(100vh+700px)]">
		<div class="sticky top-[calc(100vh-900px)] h-[900px] md:top-[calc(100vh-700px)] md:h-[700px]">
			<Container className="h-full">
				<div class="flex h-full flex-col justify-between gap-4 px-2 py-10 sm:px-6">
					<div class="flex flex-col gap-10 md:flex-row">
						<nav class="text-right md:order-1 md:w-3/5 md:justify-between">
							<ul>
								<li><a href="#" class="font-heading text-2xl font-light uppercase">Inicio</a></li>
								<li><a href="#" class="font-heading text-2xl font-light uppercase">Sobre Mí</a></li>
								<li><a href="#" class="font-heading text-2xl font-light uppercase">Contacto</a></li>
								<li><a href="#" class="font-heading text-2xl font-light uppercase">Blog</a></li>
							</ul>
						</nav>
						<h2 class="w-2/5 text-5xl font-normal uppercase">Ponte en contacto conmigo</h2>
					</div>
					<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between">
						<p class="w-1/2 text-sm max-lg:mx-auto max-lg:text-center lg:w-1/3">
							Muchas gracias por llegar hasta aquí. Si tienes alguna pregunta o duda, no dudes en
							ponerte en contacto conmigo. Estaré encantada de ayudarte.
						</p>
						<CustomEmail classNames="relative h-8 overflow-hidden sm:h-12 lg:w-[max-content] " />
					</div>
					<div class="flex justify-center">
						<AnimationIsla delay="4s" fill="dark" />
						<AnimationIsla fill="amber" color="amber" />
					</div>
					<div class="">
						<p class="flex items-center justify-center gap-1 font-heading">
							Copyright - <span class="font-heading text-amber-700">©laisladelyoga.com</span> - 2024
							Thrymr
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</Container>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>
